title: Learn how to install a git project of Lynx and how to extract an APK to share with the community.
description:
This video is done because I wanted to build the APK of the last public demo of Lynx and share it. I took the time in this video to also show how to extract any APK of an android device with SideQuest to share it to the community. 
( /!\ Don't do extraction of APK without the authorization of the company or developer behind it )
author: Learn By Playing In XR
